setFeedRoute.t.sol
├── when caller does not have the relevant role
│  └── it should revert with AccessManagedUnauthorized
└── when caller has the relevant role
   ├── given first price feed is null
   │  └── it should revert with InvalidFeedRoute
   └── given first price feed is non null
      ├── it should emit a FeedRouteRegistered event
      └── it should associate the provided feed route to the provided token in contract storage
